WEBVTT

00:01.434 --> 00:03.367
For the last time,
the best cop movies,

00:03.368 --> 00:05.168
in order: Training day,

00:05.169 --> 00:07.003
lethal weapon, and Fargo.

00:07.004 --> 00:08.704
- End of discussion.
- Wrong.

00:08.738 --> 00:11.439
Die hard is the best
cop movie of all time.

00:11.440 --> 00:13.307
One cop heroically
saving the day

00:13.308 --> 00:15.208
while everyone else
stands around and watches.

00:15.209 --> 00:16.809
It's the story of my life.

00:16.843 --> 00:18.276
I like Turner & Hooch.

00:18.277 --> 00:20.778
Tom Hanks, reluctant
friendship with a dog.

00:20.779 --> 00:22.779
That hits me where I live.

00:22.814 --> 00:24.314
No. Robocop.

00:24.315 --> 00:26.716
It's got everything I like...
Gratuitous violence.

00:27.952 --> 00:29.220
Oh, I thought
you were listing things.

00:29.221 --> 00:30.655
- I was. I'm done.
- Okay.

00:30.656 --> 00:33.124
Let's talk bad boys.
That's the perfect cop movie.

00:33.125 --> 00:35.125
Mr. Smith, lookin' fine.

00:35.126 --> 00:38.262
A hot cup of tea Leone.
Come on.

00:38.263 --> 00:40.999
Francois Truffaut's
breathless.

00:41.031 --> 00:42.098
What?

00:42.132 --> 00:44.232
Terry likes
foreign films.

00:44.267 --> 00:46.267
Mm-kay. There is
a correct answer

00:46.268 --> 00:47.467
to this question, though.

00:47.502 --> 00:49.603
So gather around
for the greatest cop film

00:49.604 --> 00:50.902
of all time.

00:50.903 --> 00:53.304
Please refrain from texting
during our presentation.

00:53.339 --> 00:54.438
(Man)
Excuse me, ma'am.

00:54.439 --> 00:55.773
All right,
so there's Hitchcock.

00:55.774 --> 00:56.840
And there's an old hooker.

00:56.841 --> 00:58.174
There it is!

00:58.175 --> 00:59.351
Come on, guys,
that happened four years ago.

00:59.376 --> 01:01.342
Shh, this is
the best part.

01:01.343 --> 01:03.144
Takes the wallet
and here she goes!

01:03.145 --> 01:06.145
[All groan]

01:06.146 --> 01:09.147
[Upbeat music]

01:09.148 --> 01:15.147
